-- Samsung Electronics Says It May Raise Annual Indian Refrigerator Output
-- B y   J u n   Y a n g
-- 2010-10-11T01:37:13Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-10-11/samsung-electronics-says-it-may-raise-annual-indian-refrigerator-output.html
Samsung Electronics Co. may increase
refrigerator output capacity to 1 million units in India,
spokeswoman Chenny Kim said, confirming an Edaily report.
Samsung declined to give the current annual output.  To contact the reporter on this story:
